+------------------------------------------+
|                 student                  |
+------------------------------------------+
|        studentname (varchar(20))         |
|          primaryKey = studentid          |
+------------------------------------------+

+------------------------------------------+
|                 subject                  |
+------------------------------------------+
|        subjectname (varchar(20))         |
|             studentid (int)              |
|          primaryKey = subjectid          |
|          foreignKey = studentid          |
|       references student.studentid       |
+------------------------------------------+


Legend:
<>------: Foreign Key Relationship (1:N)
--------: Foreign Key Relationship (1:1)
         learns
student------<>subject
